SENATE RESOLUTION NO. 94
BY SENATOR HODGES
COMMENDATIONS. Commends John Rodriguez on being selected "Student of the Year"
at Maurepas High School in Livingston Parish.
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend and congratulate John Rodriguez upon being named the 2025–2026 "Student
3 of the Year" at Maurepas High School in Livingston Parish.
4 WHEREAS, John Rodriguez has been selected as the 2025–2026 "Student of the
5 Year" at Maurepas High School, an honor that reflects his exceptional dedication to
6 scholarship, leadership, and personal integrity; and
7 WHEREAS, John has distinguished himself academically by maintaining a perfect
8 4.0 grade point average and earning an impressive composite score of 34 on the ACT,
9 demonstrating both intellectual ability and a strong work ethic; and
10 WHEREAS, John is an active member of the National Beta Club and consistently
11 challenges himself through rigorous coursework while representing Maurepas High School
12 with integrity and pride; and
13 WHEREAS, in addition to his academic accomplishments, John is a well-rounded
14 student-athlete who has participated in basketball, cross country, track, and powerlifting,
15 developing discipline, resilience, teamwork, and leadership through his athletic pursuits; and
16 WHEREAS, John is thoughtful and engaged in issues affecting students today,
17 including access to education, emotional intelligence, mental health, and the challenge of
18 balancing academics with athletics; and he is especially mindful of the unique circumstances
