1 faced by students in smaller schools; and
2 WHEREAS, John is committed to using his voice and experiences to uplift others
3 and to serve as a positive role model within his school and community; and
4 WHEREAS, John plans to attend a Louisiana university through the TOPS program,
5 with Southeastern Louisiana University, Louisiana State University, and Tulane University
6 as his top choices, and also intends to pursue a career in a math or science-related field in
7 order to make a meaningful and lasting impact.
8 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
9 does hereby commend and congratulate John Rodriguez upon being named the 2025–2026
10 "Student of the Year" at Maurepas High School in Livingston Parish.
11 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to John
12 Rodriguez.
